OL,3,CPrison drug crackdown planned after
OL,4,Cdamning inspection
OL,6,FA crackdown on drugs will be
OL,7,Fimplemented at a prison after a
OL,8,Fdamning inspection found "catastrophic
OL,9,Flevels" of narcotics.
OL,11,FHM Inspectorate of Prisons also found
OL,12,Fthat HMP Manchester, previously known
OL,13,Fas Strangeways, is in need of urgent
OL,14,Fimprovement after observing organised
OL,15,Fcrime, high rates of violence and a
OL,16,Frat infestation.
