OL,3,CPrison drug crackdown planned after
OL,4,Cdamning inspection
OL,6,FSince the inspectorate published its
OL,7,Ffindings in October, the prison has
OL,8,Fpublished an action plan, including
OL,9,Finstalling a new CCTV system and
OL,10,Fnetting to combat drones dropping
OL,11,Fcontraband into the site.
OL,13,FLord Timpson, the Minister for Prisons
OL,14,Fand Probation, said: "The chief
OL,15,Finspector's report made for dire
OL,16,Freading and highlighted the stark
OL,17,Frealities of the prison crisis we
OL,18,Finherited.
