OL,3,CPrison drug crackdown planned after
OL,4,Cdamning inspection
OL,6,F"I have visited the prison myself and
OL,7,Fmet with the governor. The frontline
OL,8,Fstaff are already working hard to
OL,9,Freduce violence and improve
OL,10,Fconditions. This action plan will
OL,11,Fensure they have the support they
OL,12,Fneed."
OL,14,FHMP Manchester also plans to appoint
OL,15,Fspecialist staff to aid in spotting
OL,16,Fand supporting vulnerable prisoners at
OL,17,Frisk of self-harm and to deliver new
OL,18,Ftraining to frontline officers to
OL,19,Fimprove the management of violent
OL,20,Foffenders.
