OL,3,CPrison drug crackdown planned after
OL,4,Cdamning inspection
OL,6,FA new pest control strategy is being
OL,7,Fimplemented to tackle the prison's rat
OL,8,Finfestation and a team has been
OL,9,Fcreated to address urgent repairs.
OL,11,FIt comes after inspectors found the
OL,12,Fprison was "filthy", with a chronic
OL,13,Frodent infestation, and many cell
OL,14,Fwindows were smashed.
OL,16,FThe prison will also review its
OL,17,Feducation programmes with the aim of
OL,18,Fredesigning its curriculum.
