OL,3,CPrison drug crackdown planned after
OL,4,Cdamning inspection
OL,6,FHMP Manchester, which houses category
OL,7,FA and B prisoners, was the scene of
OL,8,Fthe longest prison riot in British
OL,9,Fhistory, lasting from April 1 to April
OL,10,F25 1990.
OL,12,FThousands of inmates have been
OL,13,Freleased early from prison sentences
OL,14,Fin the last two months as part of the
OL,15,FGovernment's plans to reduce
OL,16,Fovercrowding.
OL,18,FThe Ministry of Justice said prison's
OL,19,Facross the country reaching over
OL,20,Fcapacity pushed jails to the "point of
OL,21,Fcollapse".
